OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry and cloudy, chance
OL,6,Fof a light shower at first. Becoming
OL,7,Fsomewhat brighter in the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some sunny spells possible,
OL,9,Fmainly across eastern areas.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudy this
OL,12,Fevening with the chance of a few spots
OL,13,Fof light rain. Later in the night,
OL,14,Fclearer spells and isolated showers
OL,15,Fdevelop, accompanied by freshening
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
