OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRather cloudy at first, with
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain spreading southeast
OL,7,Fduring the morning. Then turning drier
OL,8,Fand brighter into the afternoon with a
OL,9,Ffew light scattered showers. Fresh
OL,10,Fwinds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBright
OL,13,Fspells and scattered showers on
OL,14,FSunday. Fairly unsettled and
OL,15,Fchangeable Monday and Tuesday with the
OL,16,Frisk of further showers or spells of
OL,17,Frain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
